User & Group Management 
To create user – sudo useradd –m devops_user 
To set password – sudo passwd devops_user  #username 
To create group – sudo groupadd devops_team 
To add user to group - sudo gpasswd –a devops_user devops_team
Restrict SSH login for certain users - sudo vi /etc/ssh/ssh.d - Add a line DenyUsers #user name
